.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=18306">Hussar</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> Kneeslicer - Drunken Tsunami</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=gallerus>Gallerus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 184<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/16/03 4:55 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Bastion of Thunder corners</span><hr size=1> hope you have fun with your new ring container <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
